      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, offering precise engagement and mechanical synergy. The drivetrain is robust, with the variable M differential lock providing excellent corner-exit traction. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive Double-VANOS service and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis longevity. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for balanced lateral dynamics. While the aesthetic reflects honest use, the mechanical vitals remain sharp, making this a superb candidate for the enthusiast seeking authentic analog performance.",
